NAME

  Fake::Our - Fake 'our' support for perl 5.00503

SYNOPSIS

  use Fake::Our;

DESCRIPTION

  Fake::Our provides fake 'our' support on perl 5.00503. This is a module to
  help writing portable programs and modules across recent and old versions of
  Perl. Using this module is deprecated, since it gives your script "no strict
  qw(vars)". Moreover, this module is incomplete and limited.

INSTALLATION

  1. Copy Fake/Our.pm to @INC directory.

BUGS

  Fake::Our doesn't provide lvalue our, like:
    our($var) = 'lvalue';
    our(@var) = qw(lvalue1 lvalue2 lvalue3);
    our(%var) = qw(key1 lvalue1 key2 lvalue2 key3 lvalue3);

